title: [clips4sale] Tara Tainton - Stop and Go at My Command and More
description:
[clips4sale] Tara Tainton - Stop and Go at My Command and More
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Oh, you love playing games... my way. This time, I want to control your movements with a simple "stop and go" instruction... or do I ever allow it to be that simple?? You'll soon find out... I'm going to dictate your speed: slow, medium, faster, FASTER! And I'm even going to dictate your position. I'm going to have you changing it all up left, right, and center. You're going to be confused, in a daze, and jerking like a mad man... until I finally allow you to come. Can you last that long? The sight of me alone may be too much for you to handle.
